   ｰｱｲﾛﾛﾛﾛﾛﾛﾟ ﾜﾟ  ﾟｲﾟ     Release notes:
        ﾜﾜﾜ
        ﾛﾛﾛ   Security Engineering addresses the problem of inadequate and
        ﾛﾛﾛ   incomplete security solutions. The configuration of an
        ﾛﾛﾛ   integrated and resilient security framework is the goal of
        ﾛﾛﾛ   this course on Security Engineering. In this course,
        ﾛﾛﾛ   Security Engineering, you will learn the use of security
        ﾛﾛﾛ   models and gain the ability to develop and deploy a robust
        ﾛﾛﾛ   security solution tailored for your organization. First, you
        ﾛﾛﾛ   will learn about the traditional security approaches. Next,
        ﾛﾛﾛ   you will discover security challenges with modern
        ﾛﾛﾛ   technology. Finally, you will explore how to manage and
        ﾛﾛﾛ   operate a security program. When you池e finished with this
        ﾛﾛﾛ   course, you will have the skills and knowledge of security
        ﾛﾛﾛ   engineering needed to design and deploy an enterprise-wide
        ﾛﾛﾛ   security solution.
